---
title: Coconut Red Curry and Tofu with Toasted Peanut Rice
description: Packed full of protein, this crispy tofu is the perfect thing to serve with a rich and unctuous peanut curry! Jasmine rice with toasted peanuts will be sure to catch all the sauce! Don't forget the chillies, if you can take the heat!
